"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-culture-2024-0317-1433204-bend-dont-break-irish-olympian-frank-omaras-inspiring-story\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"We present an extract fromBend Do not Break, the new memoir from Irish Olympian Frank O'Mara.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frank O'Mara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extract\", \"from\": 11, \"to\": 21}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victory is a life well lived or a day enjoyed...\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Victory\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 102}, {\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Limerick man Frank O'Mara had the athletics career most only dream of, competing for Ireland in three Olympic Games and breaking Irish and world records.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"score\": 0.9914226558431706, \"rank\": 0.008651539264235916, \"text\": \"Limerick\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\"}, {\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frank O'Mara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999610330417309, \"rank\": 3.89684758502045e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"score\": 0.583898811325916, \"rank\": 0.7071575593771311, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletics career\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympic Games\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After his retirement from running, he settled in the US with his family and made his way to the top of the telecoms industry.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997228010476079, \"rank\": 0.00016593109641768327, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"the telecoms industry\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, at age forty-eight, his life changed forever when he was diagnosed with early onset Parkinson's disease.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"early onset Parkinson's disease\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The progression was rapid, causing severe muscle cramps, tremors, and eventually the inability to walk and at times even speak.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The progression\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"severe muscle cramps\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"tremors\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"eventually the inability\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this inspiring memoir, Frank recounts his battle with Parkinson's.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this inspiring memoir\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"Frank\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"his battle\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkinson\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you have to accept the unbelievable The event that finally forced me to face reality did not happen in a doctor's office or a hospital.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unbelievable The event\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"a doctor's office\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"a hospital\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel the true weight of my diagnosis until my friend Gary Taylor came over to check on us at home.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\", \"score\": 0.8871351948527195, \"rank\": 0.0812243502051856, \"text\": \"Gary Taylor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the true weight\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"my diagnosis\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"my friend\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary was aware that I'd been struggling with some sort of malady for months.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd followed my effort to treat my issue as a sports injury.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my effort\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"my issue\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports injury\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When my sports medicine specialist said it might be a little more complicated than that, I saw a spine-doctor to rule out spinal stenosis.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sports medicine specialist\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"a spine-doctor\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"spinal stenosis\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next up, the neurologist.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary knew I'd seen a neurologist earlier that week, but he did not know what, if anything, we'd learned.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"a neurologist\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor had performed what seemed to be perfunctory tests, nothing elaborate: routine hand motions, finger tapping, foot stomping, and basic balance and gait tests.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The doctor\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1414}, {\"ngram\": \"perfunctory tests\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"routine hand motions\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"finger tapping\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"foot stomping\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"basic balance and gait tests\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The exam only lasted about ten minutes.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The exam\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor's response had been quick and precise.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The doctor's response\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have seen this often enough to recognise it.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a slowness in your movement on the left side.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a slowness\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"your movement\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"the left side\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry to have to tell you this.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have Parkinson's disease.'\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkinson's disease\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I took his assessment with a degree of scepticism.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his assessment\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"scepticism\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What baffles me is, I came in with a running problem and I am leaving with an old person's neurological disease,' I said.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a running problem\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"an old person's neurological disease\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor just shook his head, but I pressed on.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The doctor\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am only forty-eight years old.'\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor had then proposed a way I might postpone reality a little longer.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The doctor\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I suggest that you take a drug called Sinemet, which is used to treat the symptoms of the disease,' he said.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drug\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"Sinemet\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"the symptoms\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"the disease\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you see an improvement, then you know you have Parkinson's.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an improvement\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkinson\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, then you know I am wrong.'\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know Dr Archer very well at that point, but I appreciated that he refrained from adding, 'I think you will find that I am right.'\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\", \"score\": 0.9999970917375774, \"rank\": 2.9082708837433126e-06, \"text\": \"Archer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, I have given him many opportunities to say, 'I told you so,' but he never has.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many opportunities\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On my way home from the neurologist, I had called my wife, Patty, and rattled on about having no visible symptoms, so what improvement would I even look for?\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2681, \"end\": 2686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my way\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"the neurologist\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"no visible symptoms\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"what improvement\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She humoured me, which only served as reinforcement in my confused mind.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reinforcement\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"my confused mind\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I saw it, I was just trying to get to the bottom of a chronic injury that prevented me from running and was now beginning to interfere with my walking.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"a chronic injury\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"my walking\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not have a single symptom the doctor could point to,' I persisted.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a single symptom\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"the doctor\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not even have a tremor!'\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tremor\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As usual, Patty gave wise counsel.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wise counsel\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Why do not I pick up the medicine this afternoon, and you can give it a go like he's suggested?'\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medicine\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"a go\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she said.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Why do not you try it?'\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a few days later that Gary came by.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was upstairs when I heard him knock on the front door.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the front door\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I looked out the window and saw his truck parked out front.\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"his truck\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought he'd come by to discuss the startup of a running store.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the startup\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"a running store\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't a great fan of retail, so I was a little anxious about the conversation.\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great fan\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3529}, {\"ngram\": \"retail\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a few minutes to finish what I was doing, then I headed down to the kitchen.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few minutes\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"the kitchen\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I descended the stairs, I heard voices and what sounded like sobbing.\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stairs\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"voices\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stopped for a moment to listen and heard Gary's voice above my wife's muffled crying.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"Gary's voice\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I listened a little while longer, but their hushed voices were indecipherable.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their hushed voices\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I continued down to the landing and turned the corner into the kitchen.\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the landing\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"the kitchen\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither Gary nor Patty had heard me coming and my sudden appearance surprised them.\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4009, \"end\": 4014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Neither Gary\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4004}, {\"ngram\": \"my sudden appearance\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I'd crashed the party.\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the party\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The look on both their faces said it all.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The look\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4120}, {\"ngram\": \"both their faces\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could tell they were guilty of some deceit.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some deceit\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary had his arm around Patty.\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4204}, {\"ngram\": \"his arm\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I had not known them both so well, I would have thought they were about to admit to a clandestine affair.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clandestine affair\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I almost excused myself for interrupting.\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Confused, uncertain what emotion to deploy, I just peered at them.\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what emotion\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never forget the stricken looks on their faces.\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stricken looks\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"their faces\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary saw my perplexed stare and broke the silence.\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4509}, {\"ngram\": \"my perplexed stare\", \"from\": 4514, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"the silence\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'God, I am so sorry, Frank!'\", \"from\": 4556, \"to\": 4584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then I realised what they were trying to hide from me.\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Patty had told Gary about my doctor's visit earlier in the week.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4648, \"end\": 4653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"my doctor's visit\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, you heard the news, did you?'\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I blurted out.\", \"from\": 4749, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did, and I feel awful for both of you,' Gary replied.\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he hugged me.\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was one of those long hugs, the kind given when no words are readily available.\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those long hugs\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"no words\", \"from\": 4893, \"to\": 4901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary clinched tighter before he released me.\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are strong,' he said.\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You got this.'\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to impress on him my disbelief, to tell him how wrong the doctor must have been, how little evidence there was to support the diagnosis.\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my disbelief\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"the doctor\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"how little evidence\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5124}, {\"ngram\": \"the diagnosis\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, Gary was a runner and should know about injuries.\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"a runner\", \"from\": 5181, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 5212, \"to\": 5220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was a firmness in his eyes and a resolve in his voice that caused me to repress the urge.\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a firmness\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5246}, {\"ngram\": \"his eyes\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5258}, {\"ngram\": \"a resolve\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"his voice\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"the urge\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was nothing else to do except cry.\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We sobbed.\", \"from\": 5364, \"to\": 5374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their faces shocked me to my core.\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their faces\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5387}, {\"ngram\": \"my core\", \"from\": 5402, \"to\": 5409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was especially horrifying to see my beautiful wife look so worried.\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my beautiful wife\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had accepted my disbelief because she knew it might take time to accept, let alone digest the news.\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my disbelief\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5511}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5547}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, she had no reason to disbelieve the doctor.\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5622}, {\"ngram\": \"the doctor\", \"from\": 5637, \"to\": 5647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the moment I knew I was facing a monstrous challenge.\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5668}, {\"ngram\": \"a monstrous challenge\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not keep reality at bay any longer.\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5736}, {\"ngram\": \"bay\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had early onset Parkinson's disease at the age of forty-eight.\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"early onset\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5774}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkinson's disease\", \"from\": 5775, \"to\": 5794}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bend Do not Breakis published by The O'Brien Press \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"fro